# ── 1.9.5  Power system ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
WiringMode          500   R/WC 1     UInt16    -      0=3P4W_4CT 1=3P4W_3CT 2=3P3W_3CT 3=3P3W_2CT 4=1P3W 5=1P2W
GridFrequency       501   R/WC 1     UInt16    Hz     Grid frequency 50 or 60
