PhABC_VCTPri        517   R/WC 2     UInt32    A      Phase ABC VCT primary
PhABC_VCTSec        519   R/WC 2     UInt32    mV     Phase ABC VCT secondary (actual=read/100)
PhABC_VCTNom        521   R/WC 2     UInt32    A      Phase ABC VCT nominal current
